race.description: Bj's Workwear Country Boosted Maiden Plate
race.comment: AVISTA (10) further improved for this and finds a very weak contest. Strong through the line on debut when third over 1200m at Scone. Awkwardly drawn here but looks better than most of these. MASTER SPEED (2) chipped away late on debut from the sticky barrier when fifth over 1000m at Scone. Extra trip is in his favour and expected to take a hand in the finish. LOOKING THE PART (5) massive improver at his second race start at the big odds when a tough on-pace second over 1280m at this track. Maps poorly but hard to ignore the recent placing. FINED FOR SPEEDING (1) having his third race start today and worth another chance. Came from the outside gate when a tiring twelfth over 1200m at Scone. Value contender from the better draw.
